d|55|24|N|26|38|E|display=title|region:BY_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n{{Authority control}}\n[[Category:Urban-type settlements in Belarus]]\n[[Category:Vilnius Voivodeship]]\n[[Category:Novoalexandrovsky Uyezd]]\n[[Category:Wilno Voivodeship (1926\u20131939)]]\n[[Category:Braslaw District]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2017}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n| name = Vidzy\n|native_name = \u0412\u0456\u0434\u0437\u044b\n| image_skyline = File:Ka\u015bcio\u0142 - Vidzy - 6.jpg\n| image_caption = Catholic church of the Holy Trinity in Vidzy\n| image_flag              = Flag of Vidzy.png\n| flag_alt                = \n| image_seal              = \n| seal_alt                = \n| image_shield            = Coat of Arms of Vidzy.png\n| shield_alt              = \n| etymology               = \n| nickname                = \n| motto                   = \n| image_map               = \n| map_alt                 = \n| map_caption             = \n| pushpin_label_position  = \n| pushpin_map_alt         = \n| coordinates             = \n| coor_pinpoint           = \n|pushpin_map        =Belarus\n|pushpin_map_caption= Location in Belarus\n|subdivision_type   = Country\n|subdivision_name   = Belarus\n|subdivision_type1   = [[Subdivisions of Belarus|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1   =[[Vitebsk Region]]\n|subdivision_type2   = [[Subdivisions of Belarus|District]]\n|subdivision_name2   =[[Braslaw District]]\n}}\n'''Vidzy''' ({{Lang-be|\u0412\u0456\u0434\u0437\u044b}}; {{Lang-ru|link=no|\u0412\u0438\u0434\u0437\u044b}}; {{Lang-pl|Widze}}) is an [[Urban-type_settlements_in_Belarus|urban settlement]] in the [[Vitebsk Region]], in [[Belarus]]. In 2014 the population was {{Formatnum:1684}} inhabitants.<ref>Official estimation of the population on 1 January 2014, see [http://pop-stat.mashke.org/belarus-cities.htm ''pop-stat.mashke.org''].</ref>.\n\n==History==\nDuring [[World War II]], Vidzy was [[German occupation of Byelorussia during World War II|occupied by Nazi Germany]] from 27 June 1941 until 8 July 1944 and administered as a part of Generalbezirk Litauen of [[Reichskommissariat Ostland]].\n\n==Notable people from Vidzy==\n* [[Iosif Bleikhman]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{JewishGen-LocalityPage|1951282|Vidzy, Belarus}}\n\n{{coord|55|24|N|26|38|E|display=title|region:BY_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n{{Authority control}}\n[[Category:Urban-type settlements in Belarus]]\n[[Category:Vilnius Voivodeship]]\n[[Category:Novoalexandrovsky Uyezd]]\n[[Category:Wilno Voivodeship (1926\u20131939)]]\n[[Category:Braslaw District]]\n", "name_user": "Renata3", "label": "safe", "comment": "fix", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vidzy"}
